The #narwalt10 is so intelligent that it separates paths for sweeping and mopping. It’s really amazing because it automatically detects when the mop heads are dirty too. The #robot will return to the station for cleaning and drying. Once clean the robot restarts the task. Narwal is absolutely terrific at maneuvering from floor to carpet, under, and between furniture. I’m so impressed at how well this #robotvacuum sweeps and mops my home. Narwal allows me more free time to spend with the family. You should definitely check it out by clicking the link in my bio. #robotmop

https://www.target.com/s?searchTerm=stomp+rocket (Ad) Get your kiddos outside and active with the @theoriginalstomprocket from @target. This makes a fantastic holiday gift for ages 5 and up. We received the Stomp Rocket Stunt Planes High Flying Planes with Launch Pad 3pk.  https://www.target.com/s?searchTerm=stomp+rocket 🚀
Dominic and Scotty are having a blast stomping, jumping, and running to launch the rockets.  Active play is so important for kids. Having them participate in #unpluggedplay is beneficial for their overall development. This toy combines working on #stemlearning and #grossmotorskills all while having a great time! 🚀
I love that the Stomp Rocket 🚀 has kiddos using their brain and muscle power. The boys are having a lot of fun trying to launch the rocket at different angles, into a box, and the basketball hoop. It’s great watching the boys thinking, discussing, and trying new ideas with this toy. As a mom and early childhood educator this is the type of toy I get excited about! 🚀

node.text: I absolutely love our new #Enlite10 candles by @cr8vproducts and so do the boys!  This #environmentallyconscious company is owned and ran by all woman. The candles provide a sustainable source of light by using a solar panel to charge the rechargeable batteries. The candles look gorgeous from the exterior and interior. I leave them on my windows and the sun does all the work! I am using them as night lights in multiple rooms including my kitchen and the boys rooms. It automatically turns on during the night and off during the day. Being a single mama I am going non stop all day and this is one less thing to worry about. Also, I love that they are environmentally friendly 💚 because every little bit counts. #ad #Crv8Products

Thank you @kirkssoap for sending us this awesome Back To School Bundle! September is #skincareawarenessmonth.

This is the boys favorite soap to use for their #selfcareroutinue. Shannon and I absolutely love it too. Kirk’s is a family owned company crafting simple and clean #castilesoap since 1839. They use only 💯 natural ingredients to create high quality cleansing products for everyone. Their products are #crueltyfree, #vegan, hypoallergenic, and gluten free. 

I love that they care about families and our earth. Kirk’s uses #cleaningredients along with #earthfriendly #recyclable packaging. Plus, their products are extremely affordable! You can find the 3 pack of Original Fresh Scent and Fragrance Free at Walgreens.
